<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Skyview Ranch</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A well-planned residential neighborhood located within the Northeast quadrant of Calgary, Skyview Ranch is tucked away along the northern edge of the city.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The neighborhood is surrounded by the community on the south, the 60 Street NE on the east, the community on the north and the Metis Trail NE on the west.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The homes for sale in Skyview Ranch have a distinctive contemporary appeal with sustainability being the main focus of the development.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">A typical residential unit in the community can be yours for an average price of around $340,000.</p>
        </div>
